%% 4.Delivery Zone Management System
graph TD
    subgraph Approach_Phase
        A[Initial Approach] -->|200m| B[Zone Assessment]
        B -->|Clear| C[Final Approach]
        B -->|Blocked| D[Holding Pattern]
        D -->|Retry| B
        C -->|5m| E[Hover Phase]
    end

    subgraph Delivery_Phase
        E -->|Stable| F[Authentication]
        F -->|Verified| G[Package Release]
        F -->|Failed| H[Retry Auth]
        H -->|3 Attempts| I[Abort Delivery]
        G -->|Success| J[Delivery Confirmation]
    end

    subgraph Post_Delivery
        J --> K[Update System]
        K --> L[Return Flight]
    end